hkl
------------------------------------------
The purpose of the library is to factorize single crystal diffraction angles
computation for different kind of diffractometer geometries. It is used at the
SOLEIL, Desy and Alba synchrotron with the Tango control system to pilot
diffractometers.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.5-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.54.3-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.54.3-1
  libgsl-devel-2.3-2
  libgsl19-2.3-2
  libgtk3_0-3.22.28-1
  libhkl-devel-5.0.0.3001-1bl1
  libhkl5-5.0.0.3001-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.9.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.39-1
  cygport-0.35.2-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  gobject-introspection-1.54.1-3
  libglib2.0-devel-2.54.3-1
  libgsl-devel-2.3-2
  libgtk3-devel-3.22.28-1
  libtool-2.4.7-1
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://people.debian.org/~picca/hkl/hkl.html

Canonical download:
  git://repo.or.cz/hkl.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack hkl-5.0.0.3001-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./hkl-5.0.0.3001-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/hkl-5.0.0.3001-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/hkl-5.0.0.3001-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhkl5-5.0.0.3001-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhkl-devel-5.0.0.3001-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/girepository-Hkl5.0-5.0.0.3001-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(hkl)
  /usr/bin/ghkl.exe
  /usr/share/applications/ghkl.desktop
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/hkl.README
  /usr/share/doc/hkl/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/hkl/BUGS/issue-66160af59e044b15e5d662aa382c2805d516d7d2.yaml
